{
  "stem": "490.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Being a [? witness. ?]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- unfortunately, it's very-- it is wrong to say that you can get used to as misery occurs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But most of the strength I got was from my youth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was because-- as I mentioned before, I was practicing-- not just practicing, but we lived on meditation-- transcendental meditation-- to minimize the importance of necessities, to minimize the-- the importance of having things-- have-- I mean, we never complained that we-- because usually when we're young it was not the greatest pleasures that we were involved with.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Couldn't expect much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had freedom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did the things that we wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't want to do anything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the courage I really got was the strength of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the religious strength.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It is just plain that everything has a-- even if you don't understand it, it has a meaning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It must mean something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's a matter of fact, there was-- while [INAUDIBLE] the subject, it's the same as a-- my [? monitor ?] says, how would you-- can you explain God?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How-- how would you-- you're willing to understand God?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The more complicated a project is-- I think is, the more difficult is the creator.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If somebody creates a fork in the beginning, he was no real big genius.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he's still-- it [? is ?] invention.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But how can you explain to-- to understand somebody who creates a-- the television first?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was something that nobody understands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most other people still don't understand how a computer works.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So how would you say you want to be-- understand how the computer-- the man who can-- who invented the computer?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or-- or-- going to the moon-- somebody who-- the Moon landing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Einstein-- Einstein was Einstein.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
